<item>
            <title>[LU-3937] Add option to auster to keep filesystem mounted after test run</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3937</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add an option to auster so that it won&apos;t unmount everything after it completes a test run.  This allows debugging on failure or, for auster to setup everything for you.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
